T15TD4330E:113a-1: bya sha su dzantu bindu po sha n'a ma /
T15TD4330E:113a-3: lugs kyi bstan bcos skye bo gso ba'i thigs pa zhes bya ba /
T15TD4330E:113a-4: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo ;
T15TD4330E:113a-5: / dpal gyi 'byung gnas 'jam dpal kun gyi dpal //
T15TD4330E:113a-6: mtha' dag byams pas khyab pas 'jam pa'i ngang //
T15TD4330E:113a-7: 'jam dang dpal du grags pas thugs rje'i mgon //
T15TD4330E:113a-8: 'jam dpal kun gyi mgon la phyag 'tshal te //
T15TD4330E:113a-9: blo dman skye bo mun nag lta bu la //
T15TD4330E:113a-10: snyan ngag sgron me rab tu gsal bya'i phyir //
T15TD4330E:113a-11: bdag lta dman pas snyan ngag sgron med kyang //
T15TD4330E:113a-12: blun po gso phyir chu thigs tsam zhig brjod //
T15TD4330E:113a-13: gzhan gyi skyon rnams brjod mi bya //
T15TD4330E:113a-14: gzhan gyi skyon rnams ci brjod pa //
T15TD4330E:113a-15: de bzhin bdag la'ang yod pa ste //
T15TD4330E:113a-16: dper na wa dang bud med bzhin //
T15TD4330E:113a-17: bdag nyid la ni bstod mi bya //
T15TD4330E:113a-18: bdag nyid la ni gang bstod pa //
T15TD4330E:113a-19: de ni blo chung shes rab zhan //
T15TD4330E:113a-20: dper na ka lan da ka 'dra //
T15TD4330E:113a-21: grogs ngan bsten par mi bya ste //
T15TD4330E:113a-22: grogs po ngan pa sus bsten pa //
T15TD4330E:113a-23: ma gu ta ni bsten pa yis //
T15TD4330E:113a-24: shig rnams phung bar gyur la ltos //
T15TD4330E:113a-25: ngan pa rnams la gros mi gdab //
T15TD4330E:113b-0: ngan pa rnams @113b la gros btab na //
T15TD4330E:113b-1: legs par smras kyang nyes par 'gro //
T15TD4330E:113b-2: spre'us ka lan da ka yi //
T15TD4330E:113b-3: tshang bshig pa yi tshul la ltos //
T15TD4330E:113b-4: spyod pa rnams la bag yod bya //
T15TD4330E:113b-5: bag med rgyun du spang bar bya //
T15TD4330E:113b-6: glang chen myos pa lta bu ni //
T15TD4330E:113b-7: nam yang bya ba ma yin no //
T15TD4330E:113b-8: tshig rnams brjod 'dod rtag tu ni //
T15TD4330E:113b-9: ji ltar brtags shing de ltar smra //
T15TD4330E:113b-10: gang zhig ma brtags par smra ba //
T15TD4330E:113b-11: dper na smyon pa'i bsnyon tshig bzhin //
T15TD4330E:113b-12: dgos pa med pa'i brdzun tshig ni //
T15TD4330E:113b-13: nam yang brjod par mi bya'o //
T15TD4330E:113b-14: bdag mi phan par gzhan gnod pa //
T15TD4330E:113b-15: dper na ni tso'i brdzun tshig bzhin //
T15TD4330E:113b-16: brdzun gyi tshig rnams brjod mi bya //
T15TD4330E:113b-17: brdzun gyi tshig rnams brjod byas na //
T15TD4330E:113b-18: myur bar gzhan gyis shes 'gyur te //
T15TD4330E:113b-19: dper na byi la'i brdzun tshig bzhin //
T15TD4330E:113b-20: tshul 'chos spyod par bya ba yis //
T15TD4330E:113b-21: tshul 'chos spyod pa gang byed pa //
T15TD4330E:113b-22: de ni btsun par mi 'gyur te //
T15TD4330E:113b-23: bram ze na ya'i rgyal mo bzhin //
T15TD4330E:113b-24: mdza' bshes ngan po'i tshig mi mnyan mdza' bshes ngan pa'i tshig nyan pa //
T15TD4330E:113b-26: dper na rus sbal spre'u bzhin //
T15TD4330E:113b-27: g-yon can ngag 'jam tshig mi mnyan //
T15TD4330E:113b-28: de yi tshig rnams nyan byed pa //
T15TD4330E:113b-29: dper na dbang po'i rgyal mtshan gyis //
T15TD4330E:113b-30: lha min la sogs bslus la ltos //
T15TD4330E:113b-31: gnod sems can gyi tshig mi mnyan //
T15TD4330E:113b-32: de yi tshig rnams nyan byed pa //
T15TD4330E:113b-33: bdag la phan pa mi 'byung ste //
T15TD4330E:113b-34: wa ni sreg pas phung ba bzhin //
T15TD4330E:113b-35: sdig pa'i grogs po yid mthun zhing //
T15TD4330E:113b-36: dga' bas sna tshogs tshig brjod kyang //
T15TD4330E:113b-37: sdig can de ni bdud yin te //
T15TD4330E:113b-38: dper na gling gi srin mo bzhin //
T15TD4330E:113b-39: phyug po kla klo la yang yod ;
T15TD4330E:113b-40: / dpa' bo dud 'gro la yang yod //
T15TD4330E:113b-41: don dang mthun pa'i gtam smra ba //
T15TD4330E:113b-43: de phyir yon tan dag la ni //
T15TD4330E:113b-44: srog dang bsngos te 'bad par bya //
T15TD4330E:113b-45: gang zhig yon tan mi slob pa //
T15TD4330E:113b-46: de ni blun po phyugs lta bu //
T15TD4330E:113b-47: yon tan med pa'i kha nyid ni //
T15TD4330E:113b-48: sa yi bug dag dang mtshungs //
T15TD4330E:113b-49: yon tan rab kyis brgyan pa yi //
T15TD4330E:113b-50: kha ni pad mo yid 'ong ldan //
T15TD4330E:113b-51: gzhon pa'i dus su rig pa bslab //
T15TD4330E:113b-52: zho 'dod pa ni dgun nas gso //
T15TD4330E:113b-53: drod gsher ldan dus sa bon gdab //
T15TD4330E:113b-55: yon tan dag la 'bad bya yi //
T15TD4330E:114a-1: tshul dgos pa ci zhig yo //
T15TD4330E:114a-2: 'o ma med par gyur ba'i ba //
T15TD4330E:114a-3: dril bu btags kyang nyor mi 'dod //
T15TD4330E:114a-4: bdag la phun sum tshogs bcas kyang //
T15TD4330E:114a-5: gzhan la brnyas par mi bya ste //
T15TD4330E:114a-6: zhun mar lta bu'i sems kyis su //
T15TD4330E:114a-7: yon tan mtha' dag khong du sba //
T15TD4330E:114a-8: shes rab ldan pa lus chung yang //
T15TD4330E:114a-9: dor thabs can gyis brnyas mi bya //
T15TD4330E:114a-10: dper na blo gsal ri bong gis //
T15TD4330E:114a-11: seng ge srog dang phral ba bzhin //
T15TD4330E:114a-12: kun la mthon dman med pa yis //
T15TD4330E:114a-13: nyi ma lta bu'i phan byas na //
T15TD4330E:114a-14: kun gyi lan rnams ldon 'gyur te //
T15TD4330E:114a-15: byi bas glang chen bslang ba bzhin //
T15TD4330E:114a-16: sems can kun la phan sems bskyed //
T15TD4330E:114a-17: res 'ga' rtsva bzhin zhum par bya //
T15TD4330E:114a-19: res 'ga' gangs ri lta bur bya //
T15TD4330E:114a-20: res 'ga' dmag la bab pa bzhin //
T15TD4330E:114a-21: gzhan gyi yul na gnas pa dang //
T15TD4330E:114a-23: ji lta bur ni brnyas gyur kyang //
T15TD4330E:114a-25: skye bo ngan pa yun ring bsten byas shing //
T15TD4330E:114a-26: bza' btung zhim pa mang po bsten byas kyang //
T15TD4330E:114a-27: des ni nges par grogs po spong 'gyur te //
T15TD4330E:114a-28: dper na khron par lhung ba'i mi bzhin no //
T15TD4330E:114a-29: mi gang blo ni rnam par 'gyur byed pa //
T15TD4330E:114a-30: de yi mdza' bshes rtag par mi 'gyur te //
T15TD4330E:114a-31: rab tu nyon mongs mi de ci 'dra na //
T15TD4330E:114a-32: shing shun tshon gyis ras dkar btsos pa bzhin //
T15TD4330E:114a-33: gal te blo ldan mkhas pa dgra bo dag / rab tu mi dga' bar ni byed 'dod na //
T15TD4330E:114a-34: tshig rtsub mi smra rab tu ngag 'jam gyis //
T15TD4330E:114a-35: des ni de la gnod pa chen por 'gyur //
T15TD4330E:114a-36: rgya mtsho dang ni ri rab glong la sogs //
T15TD4330E:114a-37: 'jig rten sa rnams bdag gi khur min gyi //
T15TD4330E:114a-38: 'jig rten byas pa mi gzo gang yin pa //
T15TD4330E:114a-39: de ni bdag gi khur chen dag tu 'byung //
T15TD4330E:114a-40: mi gang sems ni mi rgod cing //
T15TD4330E:114a-41: byas pa gzo dang byas pa tshor //
T15TD4330E:114a-42: byas pa chud gson mi byed pa //
T15TD4330E:114a-43: de ni mkhas pas rab tu bsngags //
T15TD4330E:114a-44: chos bde byams pa bde ba ste //
T15TD4330E:114a-45: 'jug ngogs bde ba'i chu klung bzhin //
T15TD4330E:114a-46: grogs la 'khu ba med pa dang //
T15TD4330E:114a-47: nga snyems nga rgyal zad pa bde //
T15TD4330E:114a-48: khengs dang zol byed nga rgyal che //
T15TD4330E:114a-49: sdig pa'i grogs po bsten pa dang //
T15TD4330E:114b-0: stobs @114b ldan rnams la rgol byed pa //
T15TD4330E:114b-1: de dag yid ni bde mi 'gyur //
T15TD4330E:114b-2: de phyir khengs par mi bya ste //
T15TD4330E:114b-3: khro ba rnam par spang bar bya //
T15TD4330E:114b-4: khengs dang khro ba 'ongs gyur na //
T15TD4330E:114b-5: de dag rnams kyi grags pa 'jig / gang zhig rgan po byis pa nad pa dang //
T15TD4330E:114b-6: nyam chung thabs stor de bzhin dman pa dang //
T15TD4330E:114b-7: rgyal pos spangs dang skyabs med pa dag la //
T15TD4330E:114b-8: snying rje med pa de dag mir mi rung //
T15TD4330E:114b-9: rang gi yul 'khor gnas spangs te //
T15TD4330E:114b-10: gzhan gyi ljongs su phyin pa na //
T15TD4330E:114b-11: tshig ngan so sor ldog pa la //
T15TD4330E:114b-12: bzod pa chen po bskyed par bya //
T15TD4330E:114b-13: dka' thub tshul ni bzod pa yin //
T15TD4330E:114b-14: gtso bo'i tshul ni dka' spyod yin //
T15TD4330E:114b-15: shar ba'i tshul ni dka' zlog yin //
T15TD4330E:114b-16: bud med tshul ni dka' thub yin //
T15TD4330E:114b-17: de ltar ma yin rang bzhin ngan pa'i mi //
T15TD4330E:114b-18: byams la lan med gzhan bgyis phan byas brjed //
T15TD4330E:114b-19: sdang bas gnod pa ji snyed byas gyur kyang //
T15TD4330E:114b-20: brnyas thabs byas pa de yang chu bzhin 'thung //
T15TD4330E:114b-21: tshe dang longs spyod gnyen bshes kun dar dkon //
T15TD4330E:114b-22: de dag rgud pa shin tu rnyed par sla //
T15TD4330E:114b-23: de phyir sems ni dmas par gyur ba'i tshe //
T15TD4330E:114b-24: khva bzhin mi smra kha rog 'dug par bya //
T15TD4330E:114b-25: gal te nor med bdag gi phyogs nyung la //
T15TD4330E:114b-26: mdza' bshes phyogs kyi stobs kyang chung gyur zing//
T15TD4330E:114b-27: dgra bo'i phyogs kyi stobs tshul ldan pa'i tshe //
T15TD4330E:114b-28: tshig ngan mi smra kha rog 'dug par bya //
T15TD4330E:114b-29: ya rabs tshul med khengs pas shin tu nga rgyal che //
T15TD4330E:114b-30: g-yo sgyu dad med khva bzhin shin tu mu cor smra //
T15TD4330E:114b-31: gzu lums phrag dog brkam dang khrel med ngo tsha bral //
T15TD4330E:114b-32: mi de bur gyur kyang ni gzhan bzhin spang bar bya //
T15TD4330E:114b-33: de lta bu yi dman zhing ngan pa de //
T15TD4330E:114b-34: mthon po'i sar mi drod zhing der mi bzhag / sa der bzhag kyang dregs dang khengs mi thub //
T15TD4330E:114b-35: dper na pags pa sngon po'i wa bzhin no //
T15TD4330E:114b-36: skye bo rmongs pa 'ga' zhig ni //
T15TD4330E:114b-37: log pa'i chos la rab zhen pas //
T15TD4330E:114b-39: rus sbal so yis bya bslus bzhin //
T15TD4330E:114b-40: rab tu mi gzo'i skye bo rnams //
T15TD4330E:114b-41: sdug bsngal 'byung ba'i rgyu dag la //
T15TD4330E:114b-42: dang blangs don du gnyer byed pa //
T15TD4330E:114b-43: gcan gzan gal sgor bcug pa bzhin //
T15TD4330E:114b-44: dregs pa log pa 'ga' zhig ni //
T15TD4330E:114b-45: rang gi skyon rnams ma bsams par //
T15TD4330E:114b-46: yon tan phra mos rab mgu ba //
T15TD4330E:115a-2: rmongs pa long ba 'ga' zhig ni //
T15TD4330E:115a-3: chos kyi de nyid ma rtogs par //
T15TD4330E:115a-4: log pa'i chos kyis rab mgu ba //
T15TD4330E:115a-5: blun po nor bu len pa bzhin //
T15TD4330E:115a-6: shin tu blun po la la dag /'chi ba'i rnam pa rab brjod nas //
T15TD4330E:115a-7: bya ba mang po rtsom byed de //
T15TD4330E:115a-8: bdun gyis bslus par rig par bya //
T15TD4330E:115a-9: 'gro ba bzang po bzang mo la //
T15TD4330E:115a-10: gang zhig rab tu chags byed pa //
T15TD4330E:115a-11: srog chags me la mchod ba bzhin //
T15TD4330E:115a-13: rta dang ma he glang po sogs /'ga' zhig de la chags byed pa //
T15TD4330E:115a-14: 'dod pa can gyi skyes bu yis//
T15TD4330E:115a-15: rmi lam nor rnyed bslus pa bzhin //
T15TD4330E:115a-16: sdig pa'i las la rab dga' zhing //
T15TD4330E:115a-17: dge ba dran par mi byed la //
T15TD4330E:115a-18: 'jig rten dag la rab tu chags //
T15TD4330E:115a-19: dug dang 'dra ba'i skyes bu des //
T15TD4330E:115a-20: 'dir yang sdug bsngal che po can //
T15TD4330E:115a-21: phyi ma mnar med rab tu 'jigs //
T15TD4330E:115a-22: bar do'i srid par las rnams dran //
T15TD4330E:115a-23: gsal ba'i me long rab 'jigs pas //
T15TD4330E:115a-24: las kyi dge sdig rnam par 'phye //
T15TD4330E:115a-25: rang 'dod gnas su gnas dbang med //
T15TD4330E:115a-27: las kyi rgyu 'bras mi slu ba //
T15TD4330E:115a-28: kho bos mthong gi rnam pa'am //
T15TD4330E:115a-29: gzhan yang rab tu grangs mang ltos //
T15TD4330E:115a-30: de phyir dam pa'i skye bo rnams //
T15TD4330E:115a-31: rgyun du 'chi ba dran par bya //
T15TD4330E:115a-32: rang gis ci byas las rnams bgrang //
T15TD4330E:115a-33: yud tsam pa yi tshe 'di la //
T15TD4330E:115a-34: thang cig 'dug pa'i blo can de //
T15TD4330E:115a-35: de ni shin tu 'khrul pa ste //
T15TD4330E:115a-37: de phyir rtag pa'i sems mi bskyed //
T15TD4330E:115a-38: ngan song gsum po dran par bya //
T15TD4330E:115a-39: srog gcod la sogs lus kyi ni //
T15TD4330E:115a-40: nyes pa rnam par bsdam par bya //
T15TD4330E:115a-41: brdzun sogs ngag gi nyes pa dang //
T15TD4330E:115a-42: ma lus pa ni bsdam par bya //
T15TD4330E:115a-43: de bzhin yid kyi nyes pa yang //
T15TD4330E:115a-44: ma lus rab tu bsdam par bya //
T15TD4330E:115a-45: de ni skyes bu dam pa'i tshul //
T15TD4330E:115a-46: rab tu tsha zhing grang ba yi //
T15TD4330E:115a-47: dmyal ba nyi ma gcig bzhin dran //
T15TD4330E:115a-48: bkres skom dag gis rid pa yi //
T15TD4330E:115a-49: yi dgas dag kyang dran par bya //
T15TD4330E:115a-50: rmongs pa'i sdug bsngal rab mang ba'i //
T15TD4330E:115a-51: byol song blta zhing dran par bya //
T15TD4330E:115a-52: de rgyu rnams spang bde rgyu spyad //
T15TD4330E:115a-53: thob dka' 'dzam gling mi yi lus //
T15TD4330E:115a-54: de thob dus su ngan song rgyu //
T15TD4330E:115a-55: rab tu bsgrims te gcad par bya //
T15TD4330E:115b-0: 'dir @115b bdag mi yi lus thob nas //
T15TD4330E:115b-1: phyi mar smon lam 'debs byed pa //
T15TD4330E:115b-2: de ni blun po le lo can //
T15TD4330E:115b-3: ngan song gnas su rab 'gyod de //
T15TD4330E:115b-5: yi dgas mthong ba ji bzhin no //
T15TD4330E:115b-6: 'di yi tshe ni ma nges pas //
T15TD4330E:115b-7: de ring sad dam zla ba'am //
T15TD4330E:115b-9: / de phyir dge la brtson par bya //
T15TD4330E:115b-10: dam pa'i chos la rab 'jug na /
T15TD4330E:115b-11: rigs dang bran mo lta bu dang //
T15TD4330E:115b-12: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po yang //
T15TD4330E:115b-13: bran mo btsun par thob pas gsungs //
T15TD4330E:115b-14: dam pa'i chos la mi 'jug cing //
T15TD4330E:115b-16: shin tu smad cing bshung 'gyur te //
T15TD4330E:115b-17: bi ra li ba'i dka' thub bzhin //
T15TD4330E:115b-18: ri brag 'dom gang sogs yod zabs //
T15TD4330E:115b-19: de la 'ang rab tu srung byed na //
T15TD4330E:115b-20: shin tu gting med gyur pa yi //
T15TD4330E:115b-21: g-yang sar ltung ba cis mi srung //
T15TD4330E:115b-22: yungs 'bru tsam gyi rma khung yang //
T15TD4330E:115b-23: shin tu bsgrims te 'chos byed na //
T15TD4330E:115b-24: 'tsho med tshal par gas pa yi //
T15TD4330E:115b-25: rma de ci phyir 'chos mi byed //
T15TD4330E:115b-26: nyin par 'ga' zung tsam du yang //
T15TD4330E:115b-27: zas skom gyis dbul mi bzod na //
T15TD4330E:115b-28: bar gyi bskal pa la sogs su //
T15TD4330E:115b-29: zas skom mi brgyod ci phyir bzod //
T15TD4330E:115b-30: rang lus dag la tsher ma yi //
T15TD4330E:115b-31: rtse mo'ang bzod par mi 'gyur na //
T15TD4330E:115b-32: gzhan gyi lus la mtshon dag gis //
T15TD4330E:115b-33: srog dang 'bral ba ci phyir bzod //
T15TD4330E:115b-34: rma 'bu dug srin shing srin dang //
T15TD4330E:115b-35: sa bon mu gu sdong skyes me //
T15TD4330E:115b-36: de bzhin ngan pa'i mi rnams ni //
T15TD4330E:115b-37: rang rten kho na phung ba bsgrub //
T15TD4330E:115b-38: phyi ma shes pa mdzangs pa'i tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-39: nyon mongs dgra thub dpa' bo'i tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-40: chags pa med pa chos byed tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-41: mkhas pa'i tshul ni rtogs pa yin //
T15TD4330E:115b-42: rtogs pa'i tshul ni byed pa yin //
T15TD4330E:115b-43: skyo ba med pa sbyin pa'i tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-44: tshul khrims tshul ni ma dpyas pa //
T15TD4330E:115b-45: bzod pa'i tshul ni chos nyid shes / brtson 'grus tshul ni 'chi ba dran //
T15TD4330E:115b-46: bsam gtan tshul ni g-yeng med yin //
T15TD4330E:115b-47: rnam par 'byed shes shes rab tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-48: sangs rgyas 'dod pa dang pa'i tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-49: rtog pa chung ba rnal 'byor tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-50: zang zing gnyen bral sgom mkhan tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-51: phan sems che ba sgrin pa'i tshul //
T15TD4330E:115b-52: drang po'i tshul ni mi slu ba //
T15TD4330E:115b-53: bag yod nyam nga med pa ni //
T15TD4330E:115b-54: de ni rgyal po'i tshul du bshad //
T15TD4330E:116a-2: dman zhing smad pa'i tshul byed pa //
T15TD4330E:116a-3: las kyi rgyu 'bras mi slu'i tshul //
T15TD4330E:116a-5: yon tan ldan la ser snas bcings //
T15TD4330E:116a-6: bslangs na khro ba dang bcas pa //
T15TD4330E:116a-7: sdug bsngal chen pos non 'gyur te //
T15TD4330E:116a-8: shu ma ra yi mi sdug bzhin //
T15TD4330E:116a-9: mnyam sogs dag la phrag ma dog /'dir yang sdug bsngal che 'gyur la //
T15TD4330E:116a-10: phyi mar rnam smin che 'gyur te //
T15TD4330E:116a-11: dper na gzhon nu wa dang 'dra //
T15TD4330E:116a-12: dregs med shin tu dul bar bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-13: kun la gsong por smra bar bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-14: khro med nga rgyal spang bar bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-15: kun la 'dzum zhing drang por smra //
T15TD4330E:116a-16: don med ca co smra mi bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-18: chang sogs myos pa btung mi bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-19: ci 'dod sbyin pa gtang bar bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-20: bshes med me la byams par bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-21: dge ba'i chos la brtson par bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-22: khri mas sogs blangs la bsrung bar bya //
T15TD4330E:116a-23: de ltar byas nas mang po'i mi //
T15TD4330E:116a-24: ngang gis bde ba thob par byed //
T15TD4330E:116a-25: da ni shin tu ngan pa'i mis //
T15TD4330E:116a-26: rgyal ba'i bstan pa nub tu nye //
T15TD4330E:116a-27: da ni ma bsngags ngan spyod dang //
T15TD4330E:116a-28: log par lta ba ngan pa'i mi //
T15TD4330E:116a-29: rmongs pa dag gis bcom ldan gyi //
T15TD4330E:116a-30: bstan pa'i ljon shing bcad kyis med //
T15TD4330E:116a-31: da ni snying rje med pa yis //
T15TD4330E:116a-32: chos lugs por zhing rang bzo byed //
T15TD4330E:116a-33: brkam chags pha rol mi mthong bas //
T15TD4330E:116a-34: bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan bsnyal gyis med //
T15TD4330E:116a-35: da ni gdul dka' ngo tsha med //
T15TD4330E:116a-36: sdig la dga' zhing tshul 'chos byed //
T15TD4330E:116a-37: sdig can rnams kyis thub pa yi //
T15TD4330E:116a-38: bstan pa'i zam pa bcag gis med //
T15TD4330E:116a-39: da ni mgo bregs nyams mi len //
T15TD4330E:116a-41: ngan g-yo can gyis thub pa yis //
T15TD4330E:116a-42: bstan pa'i tshong dus bcom gyis med //
T15TD4330E:116a-43: da ni khro dang nga rgyal dang //
T15TD4330E:116a-44: rgyags chos byed cing rnyed la zhen //
T15TD4330E:116a-45: sdig pa sna tshogs byed pa'i mis //
T15TD4330E:116a-46: chos kyi gru bo bcag gis med //
T15TD4330E:116a-47: da ni thub pa'i bstan pa yang //
T15TD4330E:116a-48: cung zad tsam zhig lus par zad //
T15TD4330E:116a-49: thub pa'i bstan pa gang chen mtsho //
T15TD4330E:116a-50: ring por mi thogs skam par 'gyur //
T15TD4330E:116a-51: seng ge'i sgra yi bstan pa ni //
T15TD4330E:116a-52: dus kyi 'khor los rab bcom nas //
T15TD4330E:116a-55: bde 'dod rnams kyis phan pa'i don //
T15TD4330E:116b-0: de ni legs @116b par brtag pa'i rigs //
T15TD4330E:116b-1: dus kyi 'khor lo ngan byed pa //
T15TD4330E:116b-2: ma rabs shes rab 'chal ba dang //
T15TD4330E:116b-3: tshul can dag dang sten mi shes //
T15TD4330E:116b-4: nyes pa bsten zhing tshul khrims spang //
T15TD4330E:116b-6: mi mkhas bslab nyes slob dpon nor //
T15TD4330E:116b-7: gdug rtsub nga rgyal brnyas nga che //
T15TD4330E:116b-8: ngan pa'i mi la yid rton pas //
T15TD4330E:116b-9: sangs rgyas bstan pa ma rung byas //
T15TD4330E:116b-10: zhi zhing bde ba'i dus ni zad //
T15TD4330E:116b-11: gdug rtsub mi bzad dus ni byung //
T15TD4330E:116b-12: shes rab can gyi mi rnams dang //
T15TD4330E:116b-13: dbang gyur skye bo rnams ni zad //
T15TD4330E:116b-14: de lta'i dus rnams byung ba'i tshe //
T15TD4330E:116b-15: rang gi yul 'khor gnas spangs te //
T15TD4330E:116b-16: gzhan gyi ljongs su phyin nas su //
T15TD4330E:116b-17: der yang nags 'dab dben pa ru //
T15TD4330E:116b-18: smra ba bsnyungs te gnas par bya //
T15TD4330E:116b-19: dkar po'i chos rnams yid la mi 'jog skye bo rnams la ni //
T15TD4330E:116b-20: mi chos phul du byung ba yid la 'jog pa nyid la ni //
T15TD4330E:116b-21: cung zhig dge bar 'gyur snyam nas ni 'di rnams bris pa yin //
T15TD4330E:116b-22: dge bas blun po ma lus grol zhing yun du gnas par shog / lugs kyi bstan bcos skye bo gso ba'i thigs pa zhes bya ba //
T15TD4330E:116b-23: slob dpon klu sgrub kyi zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T15TD4330E:116b-25: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po sh'i landra bo dhi dang /
T15TD4330E:116b-26: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba ban de ye shes sdes bsgyur ba'o /
